      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIPSY REGRET (2) comes off a moderate effort last start, finishing fourth at this track over 380m behind Hara's Sonya (22.54). Worth another chance. BIG EARS REGRET (8) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 2.5 lengths behind Hara's Sonya in 22.52 and recording a new PB here. Looks a leading chance again. YO YO FURY (1) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 8 lengths behind Federal Sniper in 22.36 and recording a new PB here. Has the ability and can measure up. NEYTIRI MAGIC (7) is a Hayley Wooler-trained newcomer by Koblenz out of Spookie Magic. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can run a bold race on debut.",
